          },
          "title1": "<a href=\"https://plaincypher.com/portfolio/\">Website / Software Development</a><br>",
          "caption1": "<b>Learn how you can build your own business with us and have the life you deserve.</b><b><br></b>A briliant solution to the wrong problem can be worse than no solution at all,here we are coming forward to guide and build our clients websites and we make sure that we love what we do and we do what our clients love and work with great clients all over the world to create thoughtful and purposefull websites.",
          "button1": "<a data-app-btn=\"true\" href=\"https://mobirise.com\" class=\"mbr-buttons__btn btn btn-wrap btn-xs-lg btn-default\">LEARN MORE</a>",
          "media2": {
            "image": {
              "active": true,
              "src": "@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/eb34b30a29f3093ed1584d05fb1d449ee576e1d01fac104496f9c87ca1eeb5b0-640.jpg-600x338.jpg",
