              "link": "",
              "size": 0
            }
          },
          "title2": "<br><br><a href=\"index.html\">CAD/CAM/CAE Drafting and Modelling</a>",
          "caption2": "<b>Take a look at our extensive<br> list of products.</b>\n<br>Good graphics design solutions to communication problem can improve the flow of information in society and therefore , substantially and positively affect the education , social well being and the daily enjoyment of life.in addition , good graphic design solution can also have a positive economic impact . We make sure that you get well-versed in learning graphics to design your solution.",
          "button2": "<a data-app-btn=\"true\" href=\"https://mobirise.com\" class=\"mbr-buttons__btn btn btn-wrap btn-xs-lg btn-default\">LEARN MORE</a>",
          "media3": {
            "image": {
              "active": true,
              "src": "@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/mbr-600x398.jpg",
