          "caption1": "initiative is the single most valuable skill,your actions inspires others to dream more ,learn more and achive more.your a leader to our organization we feel proud to work under your guidance ,your dedication and hardwork towards organization makes our organization to achive more.he is the person who takes a little more than of his share of blame and little less than his share of credits. we always expect to grow and build careers under his guidance",
