          "title": "<div><br></div>KNOW ABOUT US..<br><div>WE ARE HERE TO SERVE YOU WITH BEST QUALITY SERVICE</div>",
          "text": "\n<div>Our company engaged in developing magnificent website for different organization and supporting services since 2015.at Ravindra colony Haliyal road, Saptapur, Dharwad Karnataka, .\n</div><div>\n</div><div>Our current major activites are working with sister-concern company plaincypher, which recently took part in organizing 3rd national NGO and CSR summit at bangalore, we have been part of conference meeting on product quality discussion at Dennison hotel hubli with SUCO and Kodgear technologies pvt ltd.</div><div>\n</div><div>Next agenda to attend 3rd International summit at Dubai, on january 2019 and next 4th National summit at Hyderabad.\n</div><div>\n</div><div>As a result of the continously increasing demands of our clients we work with numerous qualified organizations.</div><div>Attended Quizatos event as chief guest conducted by KLE Society's College of Computer Application BCA (Afflicted to karnataka university),Dharwad.</div>",
