              "size": 0
            }
          },
          "title1": "<br><br><a href=\"products.html\">AMWAY</a>",
          "caption1": "<br>The more natural or eco based products you can introduce into your skin , beauty and personal life regimen,the more benificial it is for your skin and to your health and hygine here we are introducing \"AMWAY\"on your way! to add shine to your health and life",
          "button1": "<a data-app-btn=\"true\" href=\"products.html\" class=\"mbr-buttons__btn btn btn-wrap btn-xs-lg btn-default\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\">LEARN MORE</a>",
          "media2": {
            "image": {
              "active": true,
              "src": "@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/slide-1-copy-600x404.jpg",
              "class": "mbr-figure__img",
              "width": 600,
              "link": "",
              "alt": "",
              "title": ""
            },
            "video": {
              "class": "mbr-figure__img",
              "src": "http://www.youtube.com/embed/sOSTC6FM6Bw"
            },
            "iconFont": {
              "class": "mbr-iconfont mbr-iconfont-features1",
              "link": "",
              "size": 0
            }
          },
          "title2": "<a href=\"products.html\">LIC POLICIES&nbsp;</a>",
          "caption2": "<br>Instead of publishing policies down the throat,here we are trying to educate the customers and offer guidance on how much insurance the individual needs ,an approch that is slowly paying off, now the customers realizes the real value of fun is like life insurance the , older they get the more it costs.",
          "button2": "<a data-app-btn=\"true\" href=\"products.html\" class=\"mbr-buttons__btn btn btn-wrap btn-xs-lg btn-default\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\">LEARN MORE</a>",
          "media3": {
            "image": {
              "active": true,
              "src": "@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/3d-printing-600x360.jpg",
              "class": "mbr-figure__img",
              "width": 600,
              "link": "",
              "alt": "",
              "title": ""
            },
            "video": {
              "class": "mbr-figure__img",
              "src": "http://www.youtube.com/embed/sOSTC6FM6Bw"
            },
            "iconFont": {
              "class": "mbr-iconfont mbr-iconfont-features1",
              "link": "",
              "size": 0
            }
          },
          "title3": "<a href=\"page3.html\"><br></a><a href=\"page3.html\">3D PRINTING&nbsp;</a>",
          "caption3": "<br>To design is much more than simply to assemble, to order or even to edit : It is to add value and meaning, to illuminate, to simplify, to clarify, to modify, to dignify, to dramatize, to persuade, and perhaps even to amuse, so here we are to create an amazing 3D designs..",
          "button3": "<a data-app-btn=\"true\" href=\"products.html\" class=\"mbr-buttons__btn btn btn-wrap btn-xs-lg btn-default\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\">LEARN MORE</a>",
          "media4": {
            "image": {
              "active": true,
              "src": "@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/mbr-600x421.jpg",
              "class": "mbr-figure__img",
              "width": 600,
              "link": "",
              "alt": "",
              "title": ""
            },
            "video": {
              "class": "mbr-figure__img",
              "src": "http://www.youtube.com/embed/sOSTC6FM6Bw"
            },
            "iconFont": {
              "class": "mbr-iconfont mbr-iconfont-features1",
              "link": "",
              "size": 0
            }
          },
          "title4": "<a href=\"index.html\">EVENT MANAGEMENT</a>",
          "caption4": "&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Here we are to help you to make your event sucessfull with well planned executions .<br>Productivity is never an accident. It is always the result of a commitment to excellence, intelligent planning, and focused effort.\n<br>we provide u the excellent ideas and services to your special events&nbsp;",
          "button4": "<a data-app-btn=\"true\" href=\"products.html\" class=\"mbr-buttons__btn btn btn-wrap btn-xs-lg btn-default\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\">LEARN MORE</a>",
          "media5": {
