          "title2": "Web Development",
          "caption2": "We work on every functionality of dynamic web development &amp; database driven applications. 'EPICOP' believes in smart, secure &amp; fast web applications with ease of use for end-user &amp; business owner. We produce reliable websites that can maximize conversion rate for you<br>",
          "button2": "<a data-app-btn=\"true\" href=\"https://mobirise.com\" class=\"mbr-buttons__btn btn btn-wrap btn-xs-lg btn-default\">LEARN MORE</a>",
          "media3": {
